                  <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus target="124ra">124ra</locus>: ዝ፡ ቅዳሴ፡ ዘሰሀስሕለ፡ ቂርቆስ፡ ዘተጽሕፈ፡ በንዋዩ፡ ዘጸሐፎ፡ &lt;...&gt;እም፡ አመ፡ ጸአቱ፡ ብሔረ፡ ኢትዮጵያ፡ ለጳጳስ፡ አቡነ፡ ሰላማ፡ ዳግማዊ፡ በ፳ወ፪፡ ዓመት፡ ወመንፈቀ፡ ዓመት፡ እም፡ አመ፡ ነግሠ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ ቴዎድሮስ፡ በ፲ወ፪፡ ዓመት፡ ዘሰረቆ፡ ወዘፈሀቆ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ይኩን፡ በሦልጣነ[sic]፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፨<locus target="124ra">124ra</locus>: This Missal is of Sahasǝḥlä Qirqos, which was written with its own money; the one who wrote it is &lt;...&gt;, in the 22th year and a half after the arrival of the bishop <roleName type="title">ʾabuna</roleName> salāma II in the land of Ethiopia, and 12 after the enthronement of the King of Kings Tewodros. He who steals it or erases [its text] shall be excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul.

                        The name of the scribe has been effaced.
                     </colophon>
